groupPhotoDesc: Meet G-Dragon, Seungri, Taeyang, TOP and Daesung... or simply, BIGBANG. Since their 2006 debut, the Korean boy band has dropped a slew of blazing tracks, embarked on a world tour and even charted on the Billboard 200 album chart in 2012.
After releasing black-and-white individual profile pictures of the members, Wanna One has released a new batch of profile pictures in color!
